asset.title: VonZipper : Imaginarium : Summer of Darkness
asset.description: The Summer of Darkness pictorial is a reflection of the life and times of four young lads on a quest to blow minds, break hearts, and rip the lip. Our submission is not about surfing. It's a lifestyle piece about the never-ending pursuit of good times and the things that happen when you jump in a convertible and get weird.
